<title>USA: Hershey Foods files $500 mln debt shelf.</title>
<headline>Hershey Foods files $500 mln debt shelf.</headline>
<dateline>WASHINGTON 1997-08-13</dateline>
<text>
<p>Hershey Foods Corp filed Wednesday with the U.S. Securities and Exchange Commission a shelf offering of up to $500 million in debt securities.</p>
<p>Together with previously registered securities, the chocolate and other food products company's shelf offering totals $650 million.</p>
<p>Proceeds from the sale will be used for general corporate purposes.</p>
<p>No underwriters were named in the shelf offering.</p>
